title: Missing Jayme Closs -- Wisconsin girl disappears as both parents are shot dead at home
itunes:title: Missing Jayme Closs -- Wisconsin girl disappears as both parents are shot dead at home
description:
A 13-year-old Wisconsin girl missing since her parents were found shot to death in their home early Monday remains the subject of a nationwide search. Jayme Closs is not a suspect in her parents' murders, police say. Nancy Grace digs into the case of the missing girl with forensics expert Joseph Scott Morgan, juvenile judge & lawyer Ashley Willcott, lawyer & psychologist Dr. Brian Russell -- host of Investigation Discovery's "Fatal Vows" series, and reporter John Lemley.
